          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Self-supporting C-13 targets were made by sputtering",
                "the separated isotope into glass plates. The targets",
                "were composed of 55% C-13 and 45% C-12, thickness of",
                "about 60 mu-g/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Absolute cross section were determined in",
                "two different and independent ways-",
                " -the experimental elastic He3 angular distribution was",
                "normalized to the DWBA elastic scattering.",
                " -Use of the C-12(He3,p) reaction due to C-12",
                "contamination in the target. two methods agree to",
                "within 5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
